{"title":"正则表达式——过滤非字母字符","date":"2019-01-09T18:36:45.000Z","link":"post/292","categories":["JS"],"updated":"2019-04-27T12:21:13.321Z","content":"<h3 id=\"java：\">java：<a href=\"post/292#java：\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">String ss= <span class=\"string\">\"[^a-zA-Z]\"</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">String s = <span class=\"string\">\"A man, a plan, a canal: Panama\"</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">s = s.replaceAll(ss,<span class=\"string\">\"\"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>###js:<br><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> ss= <span class=\"regexp\">/[^a-zA-Z]/g</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> s = A man, a plan, a canal: Panama;</span><br><span class=\"line\">s = s.replace(ss,<span class=\"string\">\"\"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Java 实例 - 查找 List 中的最大最小值","link":"post/293"},"next":{"title":"git回退到某个历史版本","link":"post/291"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/292/"}